  'install.faq2a': 'Yes! Our APK is digitally signed with an official VEX certificate. You can verify the signature before installing. Just make sure you download it only from this official page.',
  'install.faq3q': 'Does the app work offline?',
  'install.faq3a': 'Yes, the app caches essential resources using Service Worker technology. You can browse the app, view your profile, and access cached content even without an internet connection. Live games require connectivity.',
  'install.faq4q': 'How do I update the app?',
  'install.faq4a': 'The PWA version auto-updates every time you open it. For APK, you\'ll need to download the latest version from this page. We\'ll notify you when a new version is available.',
